metadata.description:
DUB$TICK is a collection created by the painter and digital artist BASQKEK. This collection comprises a total of 4269 unique and randomly generated attributes that make each artwork in the collection truly unique.

The theme of DUB$TICK is centered around meme culture, particularly inspired by the iconic Pepe the Frog meme. The collection features a chaotic and schizophrenic visual style that is both captivating and playful. The combination of these elements makes each NFT in the collection a truly unique and entertaining work of art.

Each piece of artwork in the DUB$TICK collection is designed to be visually stunning and full of personality. The collection features a wide range of colors, shapes, and patterns that come together to create a fun and engaging visual experience.
